## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1746">Номер идентификационной карточки Чили</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1746">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1747">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1747">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1748">7-8 цифр и разделители — контрольная цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1748">7-8 digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1749">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1749">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1750">7–8 цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1750">7-8 digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1751">1 или 2 цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1751">1-2 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1752">точка;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1752">A period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1753">три цифры; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1753">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1754">точка;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1754">A period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1755">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1755">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1756">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1756">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1757">одна цифра или буква (без учета регистра) — проверочная.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1757">One digit or letter (not case sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1758">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1758">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1759">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1759">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1760">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1760">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1761">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1761">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1762">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1762">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1763">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_chile_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1763">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1764">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1764">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1765">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1765">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1766">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1766">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1767">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1767">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1770">National Identification Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1770">National Identification Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1773">Процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1773">Identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1774">Rol Único Nacional</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1774">Rol Único Nacional</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1776">Rol Único Tributario</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1776">Rol Único Tributario</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1777">СНИЖАТЬСЯ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1777">RUT</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1778">Cédula de Identidad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1778">Cédula de Identidad</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1780">Tarjeta de identificación</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1780">Tarjeta de identificación</span></span>

## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1782">Номер почтовых карточек для Китая (КНР)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1782">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1783">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1783">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1784">18 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1784">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1785">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1785">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1786">18 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1786">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1787">шесть цифр — код адреса;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1787">Six digits which are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1788">восемь цифр в виде ГГГГММДД — дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1788">Eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1789">три цифры — серия карты;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1789">Three digits which are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1790">одна цифра — проверочная.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1790">One digit which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1791">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1791">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1792">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1792">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1793">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1793">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1794">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1794">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1795">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1795">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1796">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_china_resident_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1796">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1797">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1797">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1798">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1798">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1799">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1799">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1800">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1800">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1803">Resident Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1803">Resident Identity Card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1806">身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1806">身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1807">居民 身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1807">居民 身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1808">居民身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1808">居民身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1809">鉴定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1809">鉴定</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1810">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1810">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1811">居民 身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1811">居民 身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1812">鑑定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1812">鑑定</span></span> 
   
## <a name="credit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1813">Номер кредитной карты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1813">Credit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1814">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1814">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1815">14 – 16 цифр, которые можно форматировать или неформатированные (цццццццццццццццц) и которые должны пройти проверку Луна.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1815">14 to 16 digits which can be formatted or unformatted (dddddddddddddddd) and which must pass the Luhn test.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1816">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1816">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1817">Очень сложный и надежный шаблон, который определяет карты всех основных мировых стандартов, включая Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, подарочные карты и карты Diners Club.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1817">Very complex and robust pattern that detects cards from all major brands worldwide, including Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, gift cards, and diner cards.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1818">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1818">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1819">Да (рассчитывается по алгоритму Луна).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1819">Yes, the Luhn checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1820">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1820">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1821">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1821">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1822">Функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1822">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1823">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1823">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1824">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_verification;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1824">A keyword from Keyword_cc_verification is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1825">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1825">A keyword from Keyword_cc_name is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1826">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1826">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1827">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1827">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1828">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1828">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1829">функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1829">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-1830">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-1830">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Credit Card Number -->
<Entity id="50842eb7-edc8-4019-85dd-5a5c1f2bb085" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_verification" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_name" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2036">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Хорватия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2036">Croatia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2037">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2037">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2038">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2038">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2039">Восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2039">Eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2040">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2040">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2041">Восемь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2041">Eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2042">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2042">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2043">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2043">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2044">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2044">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2045">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2045">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2046">Регулярное выражение `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2046">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2047">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2047">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2049">**Keywords_croatia_eu_driver "s_license_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2049">**Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number**</span></span>

## <a name="croatia-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2063">Номер идентификационной карточки (Хорватия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2063">Croatia identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2064">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации страны ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2064">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2065">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2065">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2066">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2066">Nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2067">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2067">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2068">Девять последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2068">Nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2069">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2069">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2070">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2070">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2071">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2071">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2072">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2072">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2073">функция Func_croatia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2073">The function Func_croatia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2074">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_croatia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2074">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Croatia Identity Card Number-->
<Entity id="ff12f884-c20a-4189-b185-34c8e7258d47" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2105">Номер паспорта для выхорватия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2105">Croatia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2106">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2106">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2107">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2107">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2108">Девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2108">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2109">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2109">Pattern</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2110">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2110">Nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2111">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2111">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2112">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2112">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2113">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2113">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2114">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2114">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2115">Регулярное выражение `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2115">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2116">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2116">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2117">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2117">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2118">**Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2118">**Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2119">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2119">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2120">номер паспорта для хорватского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2120">croatian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2121">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2121">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2122">Брож путовнице</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2122">broj putovnice</span></span>

   
## <a name="croatia-personal-identification-oib-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2123">Номер личного кода (OIB), Хорватия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2123">Croatia personal identification (OIB) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2124">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2124">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2125">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2125">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2126">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2126">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2127">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2127">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2128">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2128">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2129">Последняя цифра — контрольная цифра для международного обмена данными, буквы добавляются до одиннадцати цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2129">Final digit is a check digit For the purposes of international data exchange, the letters HR are added preceding the eleven digits.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2130">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2130">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2131">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2131">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2132">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2132">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2133">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2133">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2134">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2134">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2135">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_croatia_oib_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2135">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_oib_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2136">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2136">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2137">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2137">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2138">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2138">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2139">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2139">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Croatia Personal Identification (OIB) Number -->
<Entity id="31983b6d-db95-4eb2-a630-b44bd091968d" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_oib_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2140">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2140">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_croatia_oib_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2141">Keyword_croatia_oib_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2141">Keyword_croatia_oib_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2142">Personal Identification Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2142">Personal Identification Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2143">Osobni identifikacijski broj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2143">Osobni identifikacijski broj</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2144">OIB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2144">OIB</span></span> 

## <a name="croatia-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2145">Хорватия номер социального страхования или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2145">Croatia social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2146">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2146">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2147">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2147">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2148">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2148">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2149">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2149">Pattern</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2150">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2150">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2151">Десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2151">Ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2152">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2152">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2153">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2153">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2154">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2154">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2155">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2155">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2156">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2156">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2157">Функция `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2157">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2158">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2158">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2159">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2159">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2160">Функция `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2160">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2161">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2161">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2162">Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2162">Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2163">персональный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2163">personal identification number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2165">national identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2165">national identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2166">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2166">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2167">натионалнумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2167">nationalnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2168">SSN #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2168">ssn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2169">SSN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2169">ssn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2170">натионалнумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2170">nationalnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2171">бнн #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2171">bnn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2172">бнн</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2172">bnn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2173">личный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2173">personal id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2174">персоналиднумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2174">personalidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2175">OIB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2175">oib</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2176">особни идентификаЦижски Брож</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2176">osobni identifikacijski broj</span></span>
   
## <a name="croatia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2177">Налоговый идентификационный номер (Хорватия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2177">Croatia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2178">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации о номере Идентификаитон для налогового налога ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2178">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identificaiton Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2179">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2179">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2180">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2180">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2181">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2181">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2182">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2182">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2183">Десять цифр, выбран случайным образом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2183">Ten digits, randomly chosen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2184">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2184">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2185">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2185">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2186">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2186">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2187">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2187">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2188">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2188">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2189">Функция `Func_croatia_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2189">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2190">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2190">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2191">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2191">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2192">Функция `Func_croatia_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2192">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2193">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2193">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2194">Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2194">Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2195">мажсторски Брож граđана</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2195">majstorski broj građana</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2196">основной номер в соотношении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2196">master citizen number</span></span>

## <a name="cyprus-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2223">Номер лицензии на драйверы Кипр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2223">Cyprus drivers license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2224">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2224">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2225">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2225">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2226">12 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2226">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2227">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2227">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2228">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2228">12 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2229">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2229">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2230">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2230">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2231">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2231">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2232">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2232">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2233">Регулярное выражение `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2233">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2234">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2234">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2249">Государственный идентификационный номер, Кипр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2249">Cyprus national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2250">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации ЕС по национальному идентификационному номеру.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2250">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2251">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2251">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2252">Десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2252">Ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2253">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2253">Pattern</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2254">Десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2254">Ten digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2255">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2255">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2256">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2256">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2257">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2257">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2258">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2258">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2259">Регулярное выражение `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2259">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2260">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2260">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml 
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2269">Номер паспорта для Кипр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2269">Cyprus passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2270">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2270">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2271">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2271">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2272">Одна буква, за которой следуют 6-8 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2272">One letter followed by 6-8 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2273">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2273">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2274">Одна буква, за которой следуют шесть и восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2274">One letter followed by six to eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2275">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2275">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2276">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2276">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2277">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2277">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2278">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2278">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2279">Регулярное выражение `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2279">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2280">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2280">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2281">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2281">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2282">**Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2282">**Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2283">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2283">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2284">номер паспорта для Кипр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2284">cyprus passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2285">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2285">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2286">αριθμό διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2286">αριθμό διαβατηρίου</span></span>

## <a name="cyprus-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2287">Идентификационный номер налогоплательщика (Кипр)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2287">Cyprus tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2288">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации по идентификационному номеру Европейского налога ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2288">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2289">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2289">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2290">Восемь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2290">Eight digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2291">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2291">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2292">Восемь цифр и одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2292">Eight digits and one letter:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2293">"0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2293">A "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2294">семь цифр;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2294">Seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2295">Одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2295">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2296">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2296">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2297">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2297">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2298">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2298">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2299">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2299">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2300">Функция `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2300">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2301">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2301">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2302">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2302">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2303">Функция `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2303">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2332">Номер водительского удостоверения для чешского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2332">Czech driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2333">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2333">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2334">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2334">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2335">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2335">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2336">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2336">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2337">Восемь букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2337">Eight letters and digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2338">Две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2338">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2339">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2339">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2340">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2340">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2341">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2341">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2342">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2342">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2343">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2343">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2344">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2344">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2345">Регулярное выражение `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2345">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2346">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2346">A keyword from  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>

```

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2352">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2352">driver licence</span></span>

## <a name="czech-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2363">Номер паспорта для чешского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2363">Czech passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2364">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2364">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2365">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2365">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2366">Восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2366">Eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2367">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2367">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2368">Восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2368">Eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2369">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2369">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2370">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2370">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2371">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2371">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2372">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2372">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2373">Регулярное выражение `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2373">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2374">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2374">A keyword from  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2375">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2375">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2376">**Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2376">**Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2377">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2377">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2378">номер паспорта для чешского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2378">czech passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2379">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2379">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2380">цестовнí PAS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2380">cestovní pas</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2381">соответствующий</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2381">pas</span></span>

## <a name="czech-personal-identity-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2382">Номер личного удостоверения для чешского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2382">Czech personal identity number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2383">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в набор национального идентификационного номера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2383">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National identification number bundle and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2384">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2384">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2385">Девять цифр с необязательной косой чертой (старый формат) 10 цифрами с необязательной косой чертой (новый формат)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2385">Nine digits with optional forward slash (old format) 10 digits with optional forward slash (new format)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2386">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2386">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2387">Девять цифр (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2387">Nine digits (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2388">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2388">Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2389">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2389">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2390">Шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2390">Six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2391">косая черта;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2391">A forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2392">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2392">Three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2393">10 цифр (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2393">10 digits (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2394">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2394">10 digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2395">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2395">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2396">Шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2396">Six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2397">косая черта;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2397">A forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2398">Четыре цифры, где последняя цифра является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2398">Four digits where last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2399">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2399">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2400">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2400">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2401">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2401">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2402">Политика защиты от потери данных — 85% уверенности, что она обнаружила этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в пределах близости от 300 символов: функция Func_czech_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2402">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters: The function Func_czech_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2403">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_czech_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2403">A keyword from Keyword_czech_id_card is found.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2404">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2404">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
<Entity id="60c0725a-4eb6-455b-9dda-05d8a7396497"      patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card" />
      <Match idRef="Keyword_czech_id_card" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2405">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2405">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2406">номер личного удостоверения для чешского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2406">czech personal identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2407">Роднé číсло</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2407">Rodné číslo</span></span>



## <a name="czech-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2408">Номер социального страхования для чешского или эквивалентного кода</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2408">Czech social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2409">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2409">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2410">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2410">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2411">Десять цифр и обратная косая черта в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2411">Ten digits and a backslash in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2412">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2412">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2413">Десять цифр и обратная косая черта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2413">Ten digits and a backslash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2414">Шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2414">Six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD):</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2415">Обратная косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2415">A backslash</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2416">Три цифры, которые соответствуют серийному номеру, которые отделяют пользователей на одну и ту же дату.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2416">Three digits that correspond to a serial number that separates persons born on the same date</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2417">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2417">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2418">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2418">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2419">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2419">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2420">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2420">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2421">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2421">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2422">Функция `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2422">The function  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2423">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2423">A keyword from  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2424">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2424">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2425">Функция `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2425">The function  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2437">персоналиднумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2437">personalidnumber#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2440">родне Цисло</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2440">rodne cislo</span></span>

## <a name="czech-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2441">Идентификационный номер налога на чешский язык</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2441">Czech tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2442">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации по идентификационному номеру Европейского налога ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2442">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2443">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2443">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2444">Девять или десять цифр с необязательной обратной косой чертой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2444">Nine or ten digits with an optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2445">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2445">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2446">Девять или десять цифр с необязательной обратной косой чертой.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2446">Nine or ten digits with an optional backslashl:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2447">Шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2447">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2448">Обратная косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2448">A backslash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2449">Три или четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2449">Three or four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2450">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2450">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2451">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2451">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2452">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2452">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2453">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2453">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2454">Регулярное выражение `Regex_czech_republic_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2454">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2455">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2455">A keyword from  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2474">пожиšтěнí číсло</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2474">pojištění číslo</span></span>

</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2476">tax id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2479">налог без #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2479">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2480">налог без</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2480">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f2c32-2481">Налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f2c32-2481">tax number</span></span>
